content_vision: What the fuck we are gonna do. Makes my toes curl. So silly, baby girl had to get her bills paid. I aint got a fucking limit. Everybody want world peace. Feeling like I'm Snoop. Make it juicy and spiritual like a joint get my weed.
structure_suggestion_description: Spiritual, fun and games. What the fuck we are gonna do. Makes my toes curl.
text:
Verse 1:
I refuse to be held down, gonna rise up like a phoenix from the ashes,
my dreams are too big, ain't no time for excuses and clashes.
I take a hit, let my mind soar, forgetting the bullshit, can't hold us no more,
and we keep dancing, like we're on cloud nine, just living for the moment, this feeling so divine.
I keep chasing this dream, like it's my only source of light,
times get tough, but I never lose sight,
got a fire inside, burning bright like a flame,
no limits, no boundaries, I'll do it all in my name.

Pre-Chorus 1:
With our heads in the clouds, we don't need no limitations, we'll be blazing our own path,
no boundaries, just pure imagination.

Chorus 1:
Riding high like a king on my throne, taking control,
breaking free from the unknown.
Feeling so alive, no fear, just pure adrenaline,
thriving in this moment, nothing can hold me back again.

Verse 2:
Lost in the city lights, but I'll find my way, living in the fast lane,
I'll embrace the chaos each day.
Lost in this world, but I'll find my way,
chasing my dreams, won't let them fade away.
Lost in this world, but I'll keep moving,
with my head held high, my strength unproving.
Lost in this world, but I'll keep pushing on,
with every obstacle, I'll rise up and beyond.

Pre-Chorus 2:
But in this moment, I'm feeling so free, like nothing can stop me,
I'll be chasing my dreams endlessly.

Chorus 2:
Living in the moment, taking life by the reins,
every second counts, not wasting any in vain.
High with no regrets, just chasing my desires,
watching all my dreams come true as I reach higher and higher.

Verse 3:
I'm feeling like I'm on top of the world,
but I'm still grounded and humble,
Riding high on this wave of life, leaving all my fears and doubts behind,
no longer chasing the shadows, I'll embrace the light I find.
Lost in this crazy world, just trying to find my place,
but with every rhyme I write, I'm creating my own space.
But through it all, I'll keep fighting for my truth,
living my life on my terms, refusing to be mute.

Chorus 3:
No limits, no boundaries, we'll reach for the sky,
chasing our dreams, never afraid to try.
We'll keep soaring, no matter what the world may say, living our lives to the fullest,
in our own beautiful and unique way.

Chorus 4:
We're living in our own world, where nothing can bring us down,
chasing our dreams, our feet firmly on the ground.
Living on cloud nine, chasing our dreams, our feet never touching the ground,
it's a whole new type of high.

Chorus 5:
Rising like a phoenix from the flames,
chasing my dreams, no one can tame.
Rising from the ashes, stronger than before, chasing our dreams,
we'll settle for nothing less, that's for sure.

Bridge:
Lost in this world, but I'll find my way, guided by the music,
every note leading me astray.
Lost in this world, but I'll find my way, guided by the music, every note leading me astray,
no matter where I go or what I do, it's clear to see, there's a higher purpose in every tune.

Outro:
But in the end, all I need is my own dreams and purpose,
no one can bring me down, I'll rise up with each new verse.

active_struct.name: The Surprising Switch-Up
attrs: has a clear structure with repetition of chorus and verses
incorporates both a prechorus and a bridge for added dynamics
builds up to the final chorus with variations from previous ones
has room for storytelling and development of the song's theme

struct_suggs.name: The Climbing Crescendo
attrs: simple and easy to follow
emphasizes the chorus as the main hook of the song
allows for repetition to reinforce the catchiness of the chorus
has a clear climax in the final chorus

struct_suggs.name: The Opening Odyssey
attrs: strong and attention-grabbing intro
includes prechorus for added buildup to the chorus
allows for multiple chorus repetitions for catchiness
has a distinct climax in the final chorus with variations from previous choruses

struct_suggs.name: The Mesmerizing Medley
attrs: has a unique structure with instrumental sections interspersed
allows for storytelling through the verses
includes both a prechorus and a solo section for added dynamics
has a powerful outro to end the song

struct_suggs.name: The Dynamic Rollercoaster
attrs: has repetition of the first verse for familiarity
incorporates both a prechorus and a bridge for added variety
builds up to the final chorus with different melodies and lyrics
has a recognizable structure for listeners to follow

struct_suggs.name: The Instrumental Adventure
attrs: includes a prechorus and a bridge for added dynamics
features both a vocal and instrumental theme melody
allows for development of the chorus over multiple repetitions
has a strong intro and outro bookending the song

struct_suggs.name: The Eclectic Journey
attrs: has a unique structure with multiple prechoruses and a bridge
allows for storytelling through various verses
incorporates an instrumental section with a solo for added variety
builds up to the final chorus in the outro for a powerful ending

struct_suggs.name: The Unexpected Symphony

struct_suggs.name: The Epic Transformation
attrs: has a unique structure with instrumental sections interspersed
allows for storytelling through the verses
incorporates both a prechorus and a solo section for added dynamics
has a powerful and climactic outro to end the song

struct_suggs.name: The Daring Experiment
attrs: has a clear and structured form with multiple verses and choruses
features both a prechorus and a bridge for added variation
incorporates an instrumental section with a solo for added dynamics
builds up to the final chorus in the outro for a powerful ending
